01:01:45.960 --> 01:01:49.316
Good morning, gentlemen.
Do you know why it's good?

01:01:49.480 --> 01:01:53.359
Because this is the day I tell Theodore
Banner that my fellow senior editors...

01:01:53.560 --> 01:01:59.430
