01:03:12.520 --> 01:03:13.509
Uh-oh.

01:03:13.680 --> 01:03:15.716
Here's the title to next month's
cover story:

01:03:15.880 --> 01:03:20.192
"Catcher Block on Barbara Novak:
Penetrating the Myth."

01:03:20.440 --> 01:03:22.271
