01:03:28.200 --> 01:03:30.350
...and the guy who she still
doesn't know I am.

01:03:30.960 --> 01:03:34.077
- What do I have to say?
- You don't say a word.

01:03:34.280 --> 01:03:37.317
Got you. So this is it.
Tonight's the night.

01:03:37.520 --> 01:03:41.149
I have my big night with Vikki at the
same time you're having your big night...

01:03:41.320 --> 01:03:44.437
...that will ruin Novak and Vikki
and everything Vikki's worked for.

01:03:44.760 --> 01:03:47.911
