01:11:33.160 --> 01:11:35.230
All right.

01:11:35.680 --> 01:11:37.398
Now you know.

01:11:37.600 --> 01:11:40.672
I'm Catcher Block, not Zip Martin.

01:11:40.840 --> 01:11:42.558
