01:12:08.840 --> 01:12:11.479
Because I'm not Barbara Novak.

01:12:11.640 --> 01:12:14.438
- There is no Barbara Novak.
- Huh?

01:12:14.600 --> 01:12:19.355
And I didn't fall in love with Zip Martin.
