and it broke my heart to say no.

01:12:29.960 --> 01:12:31.439
But I loved you too much.

01:12:31.600 --> 01:12:34.558
I couldn't bear to become
just another notch in your bedpost.

01:12:34.720 --> 01:12:37.757
