01:12:37.920 --> 01:12:40.514
...to get a regular spot
on your rotating schedule...

01:12:40.680 --> 01:12:44.753
...I would never have your attention long
enough for you to fall in love with me.

01:12:44.920 --> 01:12:48.310
I knew I had to do something
to set myself apart.

01:12:48.480 --> 01:12:51.040
