to do was be patient and wait...

01:13:21.760 --> 01:13:24.877
...the two or three weeks it would take
for everyone in the world...

01:13:25.040 --> 01:13:26.712
...to buy a copy of my bestseller.

01:13:26.880 --> 01:13:30.270
