01:13:30.440 --> 01:13:32.317
See what I look like, and two:

01:13:32.480 --> 01:13:35.995
See me denounce you in public
as the worst kind of man.

01:13:36.160 --> 01:13:39.948
I knew that this would make you want to
get even by writing one of your exposés.

01:13:40.120 --> 01:13:43.829
In order to do that, you would have to
go undercover, assume a false identity...

01:13:44.000 --> 01:13:45.513
...and pretend to be the man...

01:13:45.680 --> 01:13:48.717
...who would make the girl
I was pretending to be fall in love.

01:13:48.880 --> 01:13:51.155
