Deceiving me in business is another.
I thought you were different.

01:19:09.040 --> 01:19:11.713
But you're not.
You're a rat, Peter McMannus.

01:19:11.880 --> 01:19:14.553
You're just like every other man.

01:19:19.320 --> 01:19:22.835
I'm just like every other man.

01:19:35.000 --> 01:19:37.673
Peter McMannus.

01:19:37.880 --> 01:19:40.440
- What do you say we step inside?
- Well...

01:19:40.800 --> 01:19:41.994
PETER:
Just for 10 minutes.

01:19:42.160 --> 01:19:43.673
VIKKl: Ten minutes?
- Ten minutes.

01:19:43.840 --> 01:19:46.070
CATCHER:
Nancy, wait.

01:19:46.240 --> 01:19:49.437
- What do you mean, you can't do this?
- I mean I can't marry you.

01:19:49.600 --> 01:19:53.115
- What?
- I can't be Mrs. Catcher Block.

01:19:53.280 --> 01:19:57.353
I can't be your wife with the kids
and the house in the suburbs.

01:19:57.560 --> 01:19:59.949
There was one part of my plan
that I didn't count on.

01:20:00.120 --> 01:20:03.192
That by pretending
to be Barbara Novak...

01:20:03.360 --> 01:20:05.794
...I would actually become
Barbara Novak.

01:20:05.960 --> 01:20:08.155
I may be the last woman
in the world to do it...

01:20:08.320 --> 01:20:12.950
...but I have finally become
a <i>Down With Love</i> girl, Level 3.

01:20:14.960 --> 01:20:16.837
I don't want love.

01:20:17.000 --> 01:20:18.911
And I don't want you.

01:20:38.560 --> 01:20:41.358
[THUNDERING]

01:21:00.000 --> 01:21:02.560
[DOORBELL BUZZING]

01:21:04.280 --> 01:21:06.475
CATCHER: What did Vikki say? Any luck?
- No.

01:21:06.640 --> 01:21:08.756
Barbara still doesn't want
to see you.

01:21:08.920 --> 01:21:11.753
She's thrown away
everything you sent her.

01:21:11.920 --> 01:21:13.478
The flowers, the candy...

01:21:13.680 --> 01:21:16.717
...the $6000 state-of-the-art
Celestron telescope...

01:21:16.880 --> 01:21:20.395
...that wasn't really for you to send
because it was mine, not yours.

01:21:20.600 --> 01:21:21.749
Oh, she hates me.

01:21:21.920 --> 01:21:25.833
At least Novak dropped you flat.
You know where you stand.

01:21:26.000 --> 01:21:28.878
I think Vikki only started
talking marriage to me that night...

01:21:29.040 --> 01:21:31.235
...in order to get me to have sex
with her.

01:21:31.400 --> 01:21:33.868
Once I did, I hardly ever see her.

01:21:34.120 --> 01:21:36.111
Except when she comes back for more.

01:21:36.280 --> 01:21:38.316
And I always give in.

01:21:38.480 --> 01:21:40.948
Makes me feel so used.

01:21:41.680 --> 01:21:44.478
It's just not right!
I shouldn't feel used.

01:21:44.640 --> 01:21:45.675
She should.

01:21:45.840 --> 01:21:48.115
But she's taking her cues from Novak.

01:21:48.280 --> 01:21:50.555
That's why you have to get to Novak.

01:21:50.760 --> 01:21:54.469
You have to solve this, Catch.
You have to squash her. Crush her.

01:21:54.640 --> 01:21:57.074
If not for the sake of civilization,
then just for me.

01:21:57.280 --> 01:21:59.077
I don't wanna crush her. I love her.

01:21:59.240 --> 01:22:01.674
All right, fine. So run with that, then.

01:22:01.840 --> 01:22:04.832
What happened to making your exposé
into a public love letter?

01:22:05.440 --> 01:22:08.557
That's no good. She's down with love
for real this time.

01:22:08.720 --> 01:22:11.109
You have to think of something.
Come on.

01:22:11.280 --> 01:22:12.998
Get dressed. We're going out.

01:22:13.160 --> 01:22:15.037
You have to start circulating again.

01:22:15.240 --> 01:22:18.038
- Where's your little black book?
- I threw it away.

01:22:19.040 --> 01:22:21.634
I don't care about sex anymore.
I just wanna be married.

01:22:21.800 --> 01:22:23.950
Well, me too. But fat chance.

01:22:26.200 --> 01:22:28.509
Those <i>Down With Love</i> girls!

01:22:28.680 --> 01:22:31.114
It's revenge against men.

01:22:31.280 --> 01:22:33.714
And it's all your fault, lover boy.

01:22:34.040 --> 01:22:36.918
That's why they all act like you.

01:22:56.880 --> 01:22:58.279
Stop the presses.

01:22:58.440 --> 01:23:02.911
I've got a cover story that'll make <i>Know</i>
sell like it has never sold before.

01:23:03.080 --> 01:23:06.197
"Catcher Block Exposed:

01:23:06.400 --> 01:23:09.472
How falling in love with Barbara Novak
made me a new man."

01:23:09.640 --> 01:23:12.200
It's my public love letter.
It's not from the old me.

01:23:12.360 --> 01:23:13.349
It's from the new me.

01:23:13.520 --> 01:23:17.274
The new man that Barbara Novak
could fall in love with.

01:23:17.480 --> 01:23:19.232
Come on, let's get this baby to print.

01:23:19.440 --> 01:23:23.194
We're not going to print. Haven't you
noticed? We have no secretaries.

01:23:23.400 --> 01:23:25.436
Every girl in New York City
has quit her job.

01:23:25.600 --> 01:23:28.433
They all wanna go work
for your Barbara Novak.

01:23:29.920 --> 01:23:31.558
For Barbara? Where?

01:23:31.760 --> 01:23:34.069
[CHUCKLES]

01:23:36.320 --> 01:23:38.311
Novak topped you again.

01:23:49.280 --> 01:23:51.669
[PHONE RINGING]

01:23:55.520 --> 01:23:58.273
[WOMEN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

01:24:07.240 --> 01:24:10.949
It's here!
<i>Down With Love</i> chocolate.

01:24:12.040 --> 01:24:15.237
A mouthful of satisfaction
in every bite.

01:24:15.400 --> 01:24:18.756
Vikki, you are a genius.

01:24:18.960 --> 01:24:20.712
Your book got chocolate sales
to soar.

01:24:20.880 --> 01:24:23.075
Why shouldn't we get a piece
of the action?

01:24:23.240 --> 01:24:25.754
They sure kill my craving for sex.

01:24:25.920 --> 01:24:28.639
The only man who could have
me now is Milton Hershey.

01:24:29.000 --> 01:24:32.390
Boy, am I glad it finally occurred to you
that you were a multimillionaire...

01:24:32.560 --> 01:24:35.791
...many times over
and we could start our own business.

01:24:35.960 --> 01:24:40.715
And to think, I came that close
to getting married and giving all this up.

01:24:40.880 --> 01:24:44.156
I was starting to believe women
weren't cut out for the workplace...

01:24:44.360 --> 01:24:47.477
...when the only problem was, the
workplace wasn't cut out for women.

01:24:47.640 --> 01:24:49.073
Banner House bastards.

01:24:49.240 --> 01:24:52.869
And the word is out that Novak/Hiller
International is cut to order.

01:24:53.080 --> 01:24:57.995
Girls are lined up around the block to
apply for the job as my private secretary.

01:24:58.160 --> 01:25:00.196
And that's not all.

01:25:00.400 --> 01:25:04.029
Catcher Block is here.
He wants to see you.

01:25:04.200 --> 01:25:06.634
Well, call the guard,
because I don't want to see him.

01:25:06.840 --> 01:25:09.832
You have to see him.
He's an applicant.

01:25:10.000 --> 01:25:12.389
Oh. For heaven's sake.

01:25:12.560 --> 01:25:14.391
At the risk of sounding like
my mother...

01:25:14.560 --> 01:25:17.677
...just stay perfectly still
and let him get it over with.

01:25:20.120 --> 01:25:21.838
Mrs. Litzer...

01:25:22.000 --> 01:25:24.116
...send in the first applicant, please.

01:25:24.600 --> 01:25:26.556
Okay, Novak.

01:25:26.720 --> 01:25:28.711
Over and out.

01:25:47.440 --> 01:25:49.317
Another ruse, Catcher?

01:25:49.480 --> 01:25:51.391
You know I have no interest
in seeing you.

01:25:51.560 --> 01:25:54.597
But you know you have to.
And you know I know you have to.

01:25:54.760 --> 01:25:57.354
You know how things are at <i>Know</i>
ever since your new <i>now.</i>

01:25:57.520 --> 01:25:59.909
I have no way of knowing how
things are now at <i>Know.</i>

01:26:00.080 --> 01:26:01.991
I knew how things were
at <i>Know</i> before <i>now.</i>

01:26:02.160 --> 01:26:04.754
You should know at <i>Know,</i>
things are like they are at <i>now.</i>

01:26:04.920 --> 01:26:07.992
We have to interview every applicant
for every job. And so do you.

01:26:08.160 --> 01:26:10.958
Or you'd be going against <i>now's</i>
definition of discrimination.

01:26:11.120 --> 01:26:14.317
You wouldn't want the readers of <i>now</i>
or <i>Know</i> to know that, would you?

01:26:14.480 --> 01:26:16.277
Have a seat, Mr. Block.

01:26:19.000 --> 01:26:21.116
Your application?

01:26:25.320 --> 01:26:28.471
Uh-huh. Uh-huh. Uh-huh. Oh, dear.

01:26:28.880 --> 01:26:33.271
Unfortunately, the secretary job doesn't
quite pay as much as your current job.

01:26:33.440 --> 01:26:36.477
So I guess that's that.

01:26:36.840 --> 01:26:38.398
Goodbye, Mr. Block.

01:26:39.040 --> 01:26:43.591
Have a candy bar for your trouble.
And thanks again for thinking of us.

01:26:43.760 --> 01:26:46.115
But I'm always thinking of you,
Miss Novak.

01:26:46.360 --> 01:26:48.555
I can't stop thinking of you.

01:26:48.720 --> 01:26:51.359
And I'd like you to reconsider
considering me.

01:26:51.520 --> 01:26:54.239
Even at a pay cut of 96.6 percent?

01:26:54.440 --> 01:26:57.079
It's only money.
Besides, I've been on top for so long...

01:26:57.240 --> 01:26:59.629
...I thought it might be nice
to try a new position.

01:26:59.800 --> 01:27:03.031
And you think you could be comfortable
in a position under a woman?

01:27:03.560 --> 01:27:05.676
I look forward to it.

01:27:06.440 --> 01:27:11.798
Starting at the bottom,
working my way up slowly to the top.

01:27:15.240 --> 01:27:20.030
Still, I'm afraid that a man
of your experience...

01:27:20.200 --> 01:27:23.556
...would be too distracted working
in a predominantly female workplace.

01:27:23.760 --> 01:27:25.318
Not at all. You see...

01:27:25.480 --> 01:27:28.950
...I'm not really interested
in women à la carte anymore.

01:27:29.160 --> 01:27:33.073
The next time I get involved
with a woman, it'll be to settle down.

01:27:34.880 --> 01:27:38.236
Well, I wouldn't want you stealing
one of the women...

01:27:38.400 --> 01:27:41.597
...from my work force just to put her
away in a house in the suburbs.

01:27:41.760 --> 01:27:43.751
Oh, I wouldn't want that either.

01:27:43.920 --> 01:27:46.514
Miss Novak, I'm what you might call
a new man.

01:27:46.720 --> 01:27:48.631
Oh, is that so?

01:27:48.800 --> 01:27:50.995
And I'm looking for a new kind
of love.

01:28:00.400 --> 01:28:01.833
"Catcher Block Exposed"?

01:28:02.600 --> 01:28:07.116
"How falling in love with Barbara Novak
made me a new man."

01:28:07.280 --> 01:28:08.872
Oh, sure.

01:28:09.040 --> 01:28:12.430
And to put yourself on top, you just
happened to have had to expose me...

01:28:12.600 --> 01:28:15.956
...as Nancy Brown in your attempt
to win a Nobel Prize.

01:28:16.320 --> 01:28:19.232
I never said a word about Nancy Brown.

01:28:19.400 --> 01:28:21.960
And the only prize I wanted to win
was you.

01:28:22.960 --> 01:28:24.154
Crazy, isn't it?

01:28:24.360 --> 01:28:27.432
After all our tricking each other,
I'm the one who wound up here...

01:28:27.600 --> 01:28:31.354
...with the love letter, and you're the
one who wound up with the scoop.

01:28:31.720 --> 01:28:33.392
Still...

01:28:33.560 --> 01:28:35.710
...I'll keep my eye
on the billboards.

01:28:35.880 --> 01:28:39.316
And maybe one day you'll do a piece on
how you became someone in between...

01:28:39.480 --> 01:28:43.758
...the bashful brunette, Nancy Brown,
and the cool blond, Barbara Novak.

01:28:43.920 --> 01:28:46.673
That's a piece I could really go for.

01:29:01.920 --> 01:29:03.194
One.

01:29:03.360 --> 01:29:04.713
Two.

01:29:04.880 --> 01:29:06.677
Three.

01:29:06.840 --> 01:29:08.796
Four.

01:29:09.520 --> 01:29:11.397
Five.

01:29:31.720 --> 01:29:32.709
Hmm.

01:29:33.200 --> 01:29:36.510
Someone between
a blond and a brunette?

01:29:39.160 --> 01:29:40.309
[GASPING]

01:29:40.520 --> 01:29:42.192
Scooped you again.

01:29:49.440 --> 01:29:51.510
I knew you would.

01:29:54.200 --> 01:29:57.829
I knew the minute I placed an ad
as an equal opportunity employer...

01:29:58.000 --> 01:30:00.958
...you would be the first to apply.

01:30:03.080 --> 01:30:04.718
And I knew you knew.

01:30:04.880 --> 01:30:07.872
And you let me in
to ask you to marry me.

01:30:11.680 --> 01:30:15.275
But you didn't know I'd say yes.

01:30:22.720 --> 01:30:24.199
BARBARA:
Vegas?

01:30:24.360 --> 01:30:28.035
We can get married there on the spot.
I'm not letting you get away again. Ever.

01:30:28.200 --> 01:30:29.474
Oh, Catch.

01:30:29.640 --> 01:30:32.871
- I love you, Barbara.
- I know.

01:31:21.840 --> 01:31:24.354
[PHONES RINGING]

01:31:26.120 --> 01:31:27.678
I'm sorry, you'll have to hold.

01:31:27.840 --> 01:31:28.955
- Peter?
- Vikki?

01:31:29.120 --> 01:31:30.951
Do you wanna marry me or not?

01:31:31.120 --> 01:31:32.758
I'm not giving up my career.

01:31:32.920 --> 01:31:34.273
I wouldn't ask you to.

01:31:34.440 --> 01:31:35.873
Then it's a deal?

01:31:36.040 --> 01:31:37.837
Deal!

01:31:40.760 --> 01:31:42.796
Well, ladies and gentlemen,
it's official.

01:31:42.960 --> 01:31:45.269
The battle of the sexes is over.

01:31:45.440 --> 01:31:47.158
What's that? Don't believe me?

01:31:47.320 --> 01:31:48.355
Well, here's the proof.

01:31:48.520 --> 01:31:51.398
Please give a warm welcome
to the coauthors of the new book...

01:31:51.560 --> 01:31:56.270
<i>...Here's to Love,</i> Mrs. Barbara
Novak-Block and Mr. Catcher Block.

